You are Oberon.
Katrina is a fellow member of the evil council.
Sevin is a fellow member of the evil council.

Ability: Should any mission get to the last proposal of the round, after the people on the mission have been named, you may declare as Oberon to replace one person on that mission with yourself.

Note: You may not use this ability after two missions have already failed. Furthermore, you may only use this ability once per game.
